  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to identify clinical symptoms and outcomes, as well as response to anti-viral
      treatment in children living in Geneva, with influenza A/ H1N1 infection during the current
      pandemic.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
